  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3643330/extras/9a46cb040cf955c983f2d7210b8323ad.avif?t=1772893998\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s a brand new online competitive platform that combines the adrenaline of high speed with the technical mastery of flawless drift maneuvers. Prove your skills against the most talented drivers from around the world</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3643330/extras/ab5aa946571ae31af72cd1551ea0aa02.avif?t=1772893998\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From legendary classic tracks to the most powerful modern sports beasts, a massive collection awaits you</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3643330/extras/934a4904c59b79053a30b67e31701a2b.avif?t=1772893998\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Change your car’s color anytime, anywhere in game without spending credits. Save your favorite colors</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3643330/extras/379ccad967b5b03c72324f842e451f2e.avif?t=1772893998\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Burn your tires across diverse environments, each with its own unique weather and atmosphere.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience a next-generation online racing adventure that blends the adrenaline rush of high speed with the technical mastery of flawless drift maneuvers. In this game, only the boldest and most skilled drivers can reach the top prove your abilities against competitors from around the world. With realistic simulation and detailed car customization, create your own driving style and leave your mark on the asphalt!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to Zenith Drift.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3643330/extras/9a46cb040cf955c983f2d7210b8323ad.avif?t=1772893998\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s a brand new online competitive platform that combines the adrenaline of high speed with the technical mastery of flawless drift maneuvers. Prove your skills against the most talented drivers from around the world</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3643330/extras/ab5aa946571ae31af72cd1551ea0aa02.avif?t=1772893998\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From legendary classic tracks to the most powerful modern sports beasts, a massive collection awaits you</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3643330/extras/934a4904c59b79053a30b67e31701a2b.avif?t=1772893998\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Change your car’s color anytime, anywhere in game without spending credits. Save your favorite colors</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3643330/extras/379ccad967b5b03c72324f842e451f2e.avif?t=1772893998\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Burn your tires across diverse environments, each with its own unique weather and atmosphere.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience a next-generation online racing adventure that blends the adrenaline rush of high speed with the technical mastery of flawless drift maneuvers. In this game, only the boldest and most skilled drivers can reach the top prove your abilities against competitors from around the world. With realistic simulation and detailed car customization, create your own driving style and leave your mark on the asphalt!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to Zenith Drift.</strong></p>",
